      "body_lines": [
        "Leader of Opposition Sajith Premadasa and Former President Maithripala Sirisena and civil leaders are currently having a discussion at the Opposition Leader's Office on forming a new multi-party government, Opposition Leader's Office confirmed a shortwhile ago.",
        "The opposition Leaders's office said MP C. V. Vigneswaran, civil activists Gamini Viyangoda and Victor Ivan and a group of SJB MPs have participated in the discussion. (Yohan Perera)"
